name: Wedge In Red Squadron 1
Lore: 'Flown by Wedge Antilles as Red 2 at the Battle of Yavin. Redesignated at Endor. Rugged Incom fighter. Victory markers show its role in the attack on the first Death Star.',
Text: 'Permanent pilot is •Wedge, who provides ability of 3. During a battle with opponent''s [Independent Starship] starship, may add one destiny to attrition or total power. Immune to Come With Me, Tallon Roll, and attrition < 4.',
